    <item>
      <title>德意志银行在亚洲私人银行业务改革中裁员数十人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/deutsche-bank-has-cut-dozens-in-asia-private-banking-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德意志银行过去一周在亚洲削减了 10 个私人银行职位，近几个季度又削减了数十个职位，以专注于利润更高的市场并淘汰表现不佳的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/deutsche-bank-has-cut-dozens-in-asia-private-banking-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:54:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗的表格：密切关注地缘政治压力现在是否更加强烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/citi-s-sheets-on-geopolitical-tensions-intensifying-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对伊朗发动袭击，但伊朗媒体似乎淡化了这些事件。花旗集团全球首席经济学家内森·席茨(Nathan Sheets)认为，地缘政治压力将在芯片、稀土金属和石油领域发挥作用。席茨在“彭博今日市场”节目中与安娜·爱德华兹、盖伊·约翰逊和克里蒂·古普塔进行了对话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/citi-s-sheets-on-geopolitical-tensions-intensifying-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:53:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桥水基金今年上涨 6.4% 后增持中国股票和债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bridgewater-adds-china-stocks-bonds-after-6-4-gain-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水联合投资公司 (Bridgewater Associates) 的在岸中国对冲基金正在增加对本地股票和债券的投资，此前风险资产的反弹将第一季度的回报率推高至 6.4%，超过了大多数本地竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bridgewater-adds-china-stocks-bonds-after-6-4-gain-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:40:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行策略师表示，利率波动正在加剧股票外流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bofa-strategists-say-rates-jitters-are-fueling-stock-outflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行(Bank of America Corp.)策略师表示，由于美国经济强劲和通胀加剧，人们担心美联储将在更长时间内维持较高利率，投资者正在从股市撤资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bofa-strategists-say-rates-jitters-are-fueling-stock-outflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:34:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于避险需求，新兴市场股票将迎来两年来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/em-stocks-set-for-worst-week-in-2-years-amid-safe-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势升级刺激投资者避险需求，周五新兴市场股市和货币走软，推高金价和油价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/em-stocks-set-for-worst-week-in-2-years-amid-safe-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《泰晤士报》称，泰晤士水务公司寻求在新计划中将水费提高 56%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/thames-water-resubmits-plan-seeking-56-bills-rise-times</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《泰晤士报》报道，泰晤士水务公司正寻求将客户账单增加 56%，为其五年支出计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/thames-water-resubmits-plan-seeking-56-bills-rise-times</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:24:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗媒体淡化以色列的袭击后油价回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于伊朗媒体似乎淡化了上周末德黑兰史无前例的轰炸后以色列袭击的影响，油价抹去了早些时候的大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:23:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曾估值 120 亿美元的快递公司 Getir 正在权衡销售和市场退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/delivery-firm-getir-once-valued-at-12-billion-weighs-sales-and-market-exits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Getir 曾经是估值 120 亿美元的快递初创公司的宠儿，由于面临投资者要求其减少损失的压力，该公司正在权衡资产出售和退出非核心市场的可能性。]]></description>
